<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Spa & Facial Protocols - Interactive Learning</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        :root {
            --dark-bg: #0a1428;
            --card-bg: rgba(15, 25, 45, 0.95);
            --accent-green: #3da87f;
            --accent-gold: #d4a574;
            --accent-rust: #d95555;
            --text-light: #f0e6d8;
            --text-muted: #b8a89c;
            --success: #6ba68f;
            --warning: #d97d7d;
            --subtle-border: rgba(212, 165, 116, 0.2);
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0a1428 0%, #1a2f45 50%, #0a1428 100%);
            color: var(--text-light);
            line-height: 1.8;
            min-height: 100vh;
            overflow-x: hidden;
        }

        header {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 3rem 2rem;
            border-bottom: 3px solid var(--accent-gold);
            position: sticky;
            top: 0;
            background: rgba(10, 20, 40, 0.98);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            z-index: 100;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 3.5rem;
            font-weight: 300;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
            color: var(--accent-gold);
            text-shadow: 0 2px 10px rgba(212, 165, 116, 0.3);
        }

        .subtitle {
            font-size: 1.3rem;
            color: var(--accent-green);
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            font-weight: 300;
        }

        nav {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 1.5rem;
            margin-top: 2rem;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }

        .nav-btn {
            padding: 1rem 2.5rem;
            background: rgba(61, 168, 127, 0.2);
            border: 2px solid var(--accent-green);
            color: var(--text-light);
            cursor: pointer;
            border-radius: 8px;
            transition: all 0.4s ease;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
        }

        .nav-btn:hover {
            background: var(--accent-green);
            color: var(--dark-bg);
            transform: translateY(-3px);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(61, 168, 127, 0.4);
        }

        .nav-btn.active {
            background: var(--accent-green);
            color: var(--dark-bg);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(61, 168, 127, 0.4);
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 1400px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 3rem 2rem;
        }

        .section {
            display: none;
            animation: fadeInScale 0.6s ease-in;
        }

        .section.active {
            display: block;
        }

        @keyframes fadeInScale {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: scale(0.95);
            }
            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: scale(1);
            }
        }

        @keyframes slideInLeft {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateX(-30px);
            }
            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateX(0);
            }
        }

        @keyframes pulse {
            0%, 100% { opacity: 1; }
            50% { opacity: 0.7; }
        }

        h2 {
            font-size: 2.8rem;
            font-weight: 300;
            margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
            color: var(--accent-gold);
            border-bottom: 2px solid var(--accent-green);
            padding-bottom: 1rem;
            display: inline-block;
        }

        /* DIALOGUES SECTION */
        .dialogue-card {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(61, 168, 127, 0.1) 0%, rgba(212, 165, 116, 0.05) 100%);
            border: 2px solid var(--subtle-border);
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 2.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            transition: all 0.4s ease;
            animation: slideInLeft 0.5s ease-out;
        }

        .dialogue-card:hover {
            border-color: var(--accent-gold);
            transform: translateX(10px);
            box-shadow: 0 12px 40px rgba(212, 165, 116, 0.15);
        }

        .dialogue-number {
            font-size: 1rem;
            color: var(--accent-gold);
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            display: inline-block;
            background: rgba(212, 165, 116, 0.2);
            padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
            border-radius: 6px;
        }

        .dialogue-scenario {
            font-size: 1.4rem;
            color: var(--accent-gold);
            font-style: italic;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            padding: 1rem;
            background: rgba(212, 165, 116, 0.08);
            border-left: 4px solid var(--accent-gold);
            border-radius: 6px;
        }

        .speaker {
            font-weight: 700;
            color: var(--accent-green);
            margin-top: 1.2rem;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }

        .speaker.client {
            color: var(--accent-rust);
        }

        .dialogue-text {
            color: var(--text-light);
            margin-left: 2rem;
            padding: 0.8rem 0;
            font-size: 1.25rem;
            line-height: 1.9;
            border-left: 3px solid rgba(212, 165, 116, 0.3);
            padding-left: 1.5rem;
        }

        /* PROTOCOLS SECTION */
        .protocol-header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(61, 168, 127, 0.3) 0%, rgba(212, 165, 116, 0.15) 100%);
            padding: 2rem;
            border-left: 6px solid var(--accent-green);
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(61, 168, 127, 0.1);
        }

        .protocol-title {
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: var(--accent-gold);
            margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
        }

        .protocol-duration {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            font-style: italic;
        }

        .steps {
            list-style: none;
            counter-reset: step-counter;
        }

        .steps li {
            counter-increment: step-counter;
            margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
            padding-left: 4rem;
            position: relative;
            animation: slideInLeft 0.6s ease-out;
            animation-fill-mode: both;
        }

        .steps li:nth-child(1) { animation-delay: 0.1s; }
        .steps li:nth-child(2) { animation-delay: 0.2s; }
        .steps li:nth-child(3) { animation-delay: 0.3s; }
        .steps li:nth-child(4) { animation-delay: 0.4s; }
        .steps li:nth-child(5) { animation-delay: 0.5s; }
        .steps li:nth-child(6) { animation-delay: 0.6s; }

        .steps li::before {
            content: counter(step-counter);
            position: absolute;
            left: 0;
            top: 0;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent-gold), var(--accent-rust));
            color: var(--dark-bg);
            width: 3rem;
            height: 3rem;
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 1.3rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(212, 165, 116, 0.3);
        }

        .step-action {
            color: var(--text-light);
            margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
            font-size: 1.3rem;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .step-dialogue {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(212, 165, 116, 0.15) 0%, rgba(212, 165, 116, 0.05) 100%);
            padding: 1.2rem;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin-top: 0.8rem;
            font-style: italic;
            color: var(--text-light);
            border-left: 4px solid var(--accent-gold);
            font-size: 1.15rem;
            line-height: 1.8;
        }

        .client-response {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(217, 85, 85, 0.15) 0%, rgba(217, 85, 85, 0.05) 100%);
            padding: 1.2rem;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin-top: 0.8rem;
            font-style: italic;
            color: var(--text-light);
            border-left: 4px solid var(--accent-rust);
            font-size: 1.15rem;
            line-height: 1.8;
        }

        /* QUIZ SECTION */
        .quiz-container {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(61, 168, 127, 0.1) 0%, rgba(212, 165, 116, 0.05) 100%);
            border: 2px solid var(--subtle-border);
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 3rem;
            margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            animation: fadeInScale 0.6s ease-in;
        }

        .quiz-scenario {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(61, 168, 127, 0.2) 0%, rgba(61, 168, 127, 0.08) 100%);
            padding: 2.5rem;
            border-radius: 12px;
            margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
            border-left: 6px solid var(--accent-green);
            font-size: 1.35rem;
            line-height: 2;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(61, 168, 127, 0.1);
        }

        .quiz-question {
            color: var(--text-light);
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            line-height: 1.9;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .options {
            list-style: none;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 1.2rem;
        }

        .option {
            padding: 1.5rem;
            background: rgba(212, 165, 116, 0.08);
            border: 2px solid rgba(212, 165, 116, 0.3);
            border-radius: 8px;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.4s ease;
            color: var(--text-light);
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            min-height: 80px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .option:hover {
            background: rgba(212, 165, 116, 0.2);
            border-color: var(--accent-gold);
            transform: translateX(15px);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(212, 165, 116, 0.2);
        }

        .option input[type="radio"] {
            margin-right: 1.5rem;
            width: 24px;
            height: 24px;
            accent-color: var(--accent-gold);
            cursor: pointer;
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }

        .option label {
            cursor: pointer;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            width: 100%;
        }

        .feedback {
            margin-top: 2rem;
            padding: 1.5rem;
            border-radius: 8px;
            display: none;
            font-size: 1.25rem;
            line-height: 1.9;
            animation: slideInLeft 0.4s ease-out;
        }

        .feedback.show {
            display: block;
        }

        .feedback.correct {
            background: rgba(107, 166, 143, 0.25);
            border-left: 5px solid var(--success);
            color: #a8d5c4;
        }

        .feedback.incorrect {
            background: rgba(217, 125, 125, 0.25);
            border-left: 5px solid var(--warning);
            color: #d7a5a5;
        }

        .quiz-button {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent-green), #2d8f6f);
            color: var(--dark-bg);
            border: none;
            padding: 1.2rem 3rem;
            border-radius: 8px;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-weight: 700;
            transition: all 0.4s ease;
            margin-top: 2rem;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(61, 168, 127, 0.3);
        }

        .quiz-button:hover {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2d8f6f, var(--accent-green));
            transform: translateY(-4px);
            box-shadow: 0 12px 30px rgba(61, 168, 127, 0.5);
        }

        .progress {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(61, 168, 127, 0.2), rgba(212, 165, 116, 0.1));
            padding: 2rem;
            border-radius: 12px;
            margin-bottom: 3rem;
            text-align: center;
            border: 2px solid var(--subtle-border);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(61, 168, 127, 0.1);
        }

        .progress-text {
            font-size: 1.4rem;
            color: var(--text-light);
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .progress-bar {
            width: 100%;
            height: 12px;
            background: rgba(212, 165, 116, 0.2);
            border-radius: 6px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: inset 0 2px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
        }

        .progress-fill {
            height: 100%;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--accent-green), var(--accent-gold), var(--accent-rust));
            border-radius: 6px;
            transition: width 0.5s ease;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(212, 165, 116, 0.5);
        }

        .score-summary {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 3rem;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(61, 168, 127, 0.15), rgba(212, 165, 116, 0.08));
            border: 2px solid var(--subtle-border);
            border-radius: 12px;
            display: none;
            animation: slideInScale 0.6s ease-in;
        }

        .score-summary.show {
            display: block;
        }

        .final-score {
            font-size: 4.5rem;
            font-weight: 300;
            color: var(--accent-gold);
            margin: 1.5rem 0;
            text-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(212, 165, 116, 0.3);
            animation: pulse 2s infinite;
        }

        .score-message {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            color: var(--text-light);
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            line-height: 1.9;
        }

        .restart-btn {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent-gold), #c49436);
            color: var(--dark-bg);
            border: none;
            padding: 1.2rem 3rem;
            border-radius: 8px;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-weight: 700;
            transition: all 0.4s ease;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(212, 165, 116, 0.3);
        }

        .restart-btn:hover {
            transform: translateY(-4px);
            box-shadow: 0 12px 30px rgba(212, 165, 116, 0.5);
        }

        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 3rem;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            border-top: 2px solid var(--subtle-border);
            margin-top: 4rem;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
        }

        .section-intro {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(212, 165, 116, 0.15), rgba(61, 168, 127, 0.1));
            padding: 2.5rem;
            border-radius: 12px;
            margin-bottom: 3rem;
            border-left: 6px solid var(--accent-gold);
            font-size: 1.3rem;
            line-height: 1.9;
        }

        .dialogue-count {
            display: inline-block;
            background: var(--accent-gold);
            color: var(--dark-bg);
            padding: 0.5rem 1.2rem;
            border-radius: 6px;
            margin: 1rem 0;
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
        }

        @keyframes slideInScale {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: scale(0.92);
            }
            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: scale(1);
            }
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            h1 { font-size: 2.5rem; }
            h2 { font-size: 2rem; }
            .nav-btn { padding: 0.8rem 1.5rem; font-size: 1rem; }
            .container { padding: 1.5rem; }
            .dialogue-card { padding: 1.5rem; }
            .quiz-container { padding: 1.5rem; }
            .speaker { font-size: 1.1rem; }
            .dialogue-text { font-size: 1.1rem; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <h1>✨ SPA & FACIAL PROTOCOLS ✨</h1>
        <p class="subtitle">Interactive English Learning for Estheticians | Professional Level B1</p>
        <nav>
            <button class="nav-btn active" onclick="showSection('dialogues')">💬 Dialogues</button>
            <button class="nav-btn" onclick="showSection('protocols')">📋 Protocols</button>
            <button class="nav-btn" onclick="showSection('quiz')">🎯 Quiz</button>
        </nav>
    </header>

    <div class="container">
        <!-- DIALOGUES SECTION -->
        <section id="dialogues" class="section active">
            <h2>Common Cabin Dialogues</h2>
            <div class="section-intro">
                <strong>Learn 15 authentic conversations</strong> that happen in a spa cabin during facial and massage treatments. 
                Each dialogue teaches you how to communicate professionally in English about comfort, skin concerns, products, and aftercare.
                <div class="dialogue-count">15 Complete Dialogues</div>
            </div>

            <!-- Dialogue 1 -->
            <div class="dialogue-card">
                <div class="dialogue-number">Dialogue 1 – Booking & Arrival</div>
                <div class="dialogue-scenario">Client calls to book a facial appointment</div>
                <div class="speaker">Receptionist</div>
                <div class="dialogue-text">"Good morning! Thank you for calling our spa. How can I help you today?"</div>
                <div class="speaker client">Client</div>
                <div class="dialogue-text">"Hi, I'd like to book a facial. Do you have any available times this week?"</div>
                <div class="speaker">Receptionist</div>
                <div class="dialogue-text">"Of course! We have several slots available. What day would you prefer? We're open Tuesday through Saturday."</div>
                <div class="speaker client">Client</div>
                <div class="dialogue-text">"I've been working long hours lately, so I really need some relaxation. How long does a basic facial take?"</div>
                <div class="speaker">Receptionist</div>
                <div class="dialogue-text">"Our signature facial is 60 minutes, and it will definitely help you unwind. Shall I put you down for this Saturday at 2 PM?"</div>
            </div>

            <!-- Dialogue 2 -->
            <div class="dialogue-card">
                <div class="dialogue-number">Dialogue 2 – Skin Concerns</div>
                <div class="dialogue-scenario">Esthetician discusses skin type during consultation</div>
                <div class="speaker">Esthetician</div>
                <div class="dialogue-text">"I'm going to analyze your skin now. Have you noticed any changes recently? Is it feeling dry, oily, or sensitive?"</div>
                <div class="speaker client">Client</div>
                <div class="dialogue-text">"Lately, I've been getting some breakouts on my chin. I'm not sure if it's hormonal or the products I'm using."</div>
                <div class="speaker">Esthetician</div>
                <div class="dialogue-text">"That's quite common. I can see some congestion in that area. Don't worry—we'll address that today. Have you used any new products recently?"</div>
                <div class="speaker client">Client</div>
                <div class="dialogue-text">"Yes, I started using a new moisturizer about two weeks ago. Could that have caused it?"</div>
                <div class="speaker">Esthetician</div>
                <div class="dialogue-text">"It's possible. Sometimes our skin needs time to adjust. Let's focus on balancing your skin today, and I'll recommend a gentler routine for you."</div>
            </div>

            <!-- Dialogue 3 -->
            <div class="dialogue-card">
                <div class="dialogue-number">Dialogue 3 – Temperature & Comfort</div>
                <div class="dialogue-scenario">Checking client comfort with water temperature</div>
                <div class="speaker">Esthetician</div>
                <div class="dialogue-text">"I'm about to cleanse your face with warm water. Let me know if the temperature is okay for you."</div>
                <div class="speaker client">Client</div>
                <div class="dialogue-text">"Oh, that's a bit too hot. Could you make it a little cooler?"</div>
                <div class="speaker">Esthetician</div>
                <div class="dialogue-text">"Absolutely! I'll adjust it right away. How's this temperature? Better?"</div>
                <div class="speaker client">Client</div>
                <div class="dialogue-text">"Yes, that's perfect. Much better. Thank you!"</div>
            </div>

            <!-- Dialogue 4 -->
            <div class="dialogue-card">
                <div class="dialogue-number">Dialogue 4 – Discomfort During Treatment</div>
                <div class="dialogue-scenario">Client experiences tenderness during extraction</div>
                <div class="speaker">Esthetician</div>
                <div class="dialogue-text">"I'm going to start with gentle extractions now. This area has some congestion, but I'll be very careful."</div>
                <div class="speaker client">Client</div>
                <div class="dialogue-text">"Ouch! That one hurt. Is this normal?"</div>
                <div class="speaker">Esthetician</div>
                <div class="dialogue-text">"Some sensitivity is normal, especially in congested areas. I've finished with that spot. Tell me if you'd like me to slow down or use a lighter touch."</div>
                <div class="speaker client">Client</div>
                <div class="dialogue-text">"Okay, maybe just a bit lighter would be better."</div>
                <div class="speaker">Esthetician</div>
                <div class="dialogue-text">"No problem at all. I'm adjusting my pressure now. Let's move to the next area at a slower pace."</div>
            </div>

            <!-- Dialogue 5 -->
            <div class="dialogue-card">
                <div class="dialogue-number">Dialogue 5 – Mask Application</div>
                <div class="dialogue-scenario">Introducing the facial mask treatment</div>
                <div class="speaker">Esthetician</div>
                <div class="dialogue-text">"Now I'm going to apply a hydrating mask. It's going to feel cool and refreshing on your skin."</div>
                <div class="speaker client">Client</div>
                <div class="dialogue-text">"What's in the mask? Will it cause any irritation?"</div>
                <div class="speaker">Esthetician</div>
                <div class="dialogue-text">"This is a gentle seaweed-based mask with chamomile and aloe. It's soothing and won't irritate your skin. I've already tested your patch, and it's safe."</div>
                <div class="speaker client">Client</div>
                <div class="dialogue-text">"Okay, I trust you. It does feel nice and cool!"</div>
            </div>

            <!-- Dialogue 6 -->
            <div class="dialogue-card">
                <div class="dialogue-number">Dialogue 6 – Steam & Heat Warning</div>
                <div class="dialogue-scenario">Warning client about upcoming steam treatment</div>
                <div class="speaker">Esthetician</div>
                <div class="dialogue-text">"I'm about to use the facial steamer. The steam will open your pores and help the products penetrate deeper. It's going to be warm, so let me know if it's too much."</div>
                <div class="speaker client">Client</div>
                <div class="dialogue-text">"How long will you use it for?"</div>
                <div class="speaker">Esthetician</div>
                <div class="dialogue-text">"Just about 5 minutes. I'll keep it at a comfortable distance. If you feel too hot, I'll move it further away. Ready?"</div>
                <div class="speaker client">Client</div>
                <div class="dialogue-text">"Yes, I'm ready. This is so relaxing!"</div>
            </div>

            <!-- Dialogue 7 -->
            <div class="dialogue-card">
                <div class="dialogue-number">Dialogue 7 – Allergies & Sensitivities</div>
                <div class="dialogue-scenario">Discussing allergies before treatment</div>
                <div class="speaker">Esthetician</div>
                <div class="dialogue-text">"Before we proceed, I need to ask: Do you have any allergies or sensitivities to skincare products? Any fragrances or ingredients you want to avoid?"</div>
                <div class="speaker client">Client</div>
                <div class="dialogue-text">"I'm allergic to nuts, and I've had bad reactions to products with salicylic acid before."</div>
                <div class="speaker">Esthetician</div>
                <div class="dialogue-text">"Thank you for letting me know. I've made a note of this. All the products I'll use today are nut-free and don't contain any salicylic acid. You'll be completely safe."</div>
                <div class="speaker client">Client</div>
                <div class="dialogue-text">"Great, I appreciate that. I feel confident now."</div>
            </div>

            <!-- Dialogue 8 -->
            <div class="dialogue-card">
                <div class="dialogue-number">Dialogue 8 – Pressure Preference</div>
                <div class="dialogue-scenario">Client adjusts massage pressure</div>
                <div class="speaker">Esthetician</div>
